'''Michalakis Zambellas''' ({{lang-el|Μιχαλάκης Ζαμπέλας}}) is a [[Cyprus|Cypriot]] politician and businessman. He was the Mayor of [[Nicosia]]<ref>{{cite news|quote= Answering a question he said that we did not meet with Nicosia Mayor Michalakis Zambellas to discuss the issue.|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=NewsLibrary&p_multi=BBAB&d_place=BBAB&p_theme=newslibrary2&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=10E40EB8259C4008&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=Greek Cypriot, Turkish Cypriot parties ready for peace deal|date=December 1, 2005|work=[[Cyprus News Agency]] via [[BBC]]|accessdate=26 June 2011}}</ref> and also the General Manager of [[PricewaterhouseCoopers]] Cyprus.

